name: IOBluetoothHandsFreeAudioGatewayDelegate
desc: A set of optional methods for receiving information about status changes for a connected Bluetooth hands-free phone or headset.

items.name: func handsFree(IOBluetoothHandsFreeAudioGateway!, hangup: NSNumber!)
items.desc: Tells the delegate the connected Bluetooth hands-free phone or headset is sending a hang-up signal.

items.name: func handsFree(IOBluetoothHandsFreeAudioGateway!, redial: NSNumber!)
items.desc: Tells the delegate the connected Bluetooth hands-free phone or headset is redialing the last phone number.
